  "texts": [
    "The features extracted by the CNNs were complemented by DWT, enhancing their spatial and frequency domain representation.",
    "The decomposition of feature maps by the DWT into approximation and detail coefficients retained the critical information while reducing much noise.",
    "These processed features were forwarded to a Support Vector Machine classifier for robust multiclass classification.",
    "The basic principle of SVM consists of nonlinearly separable data with complex classes, for instance hemorrhoids and polyps consist as one class for the dataset.",
    "In this regard, SVM employed the Radial basis function RBF kernel: tistique, where hyperparameters consisted of the regularization parameter C = 1.0 and the kernel coefficient γ = 0.1 optimized by grid search."
  ],
